68  //Generic less comparator
69  template<typename Char, typename CaseNormalizer>
70  bool operator< (const text_delaf_entry_filter<Char, CaseNormalizer>& def1, const text_delaf_entry_filter<Char, CaseNormalizer>& def2)
71  {
72  if (def1.get_type() < def2.get_type())
73  return true;
74  if (def1.get_type() > def2.get_type())
75  return false;
76  return def1.same_type_less(def2);
77  }

99  public:
100  union_text_delaf_entry_filter(): base_type(), delaf_entry_filters()
101  {}

103  virtual delaf_entry_filter_type get_type() const
104  { return UNION_DELAF_ENTRY_FILTER; }
105 
106  virtual bool match(const typename text_delaf<Char, CaseNormalizer>::entry &e) const
107  {
108  typename ptr_list<text_delaf_entry_filter<Char, CaseNormalizer> >::const_iterator i(delaf_entry_filters.begin());
109  for (; i != delaf_entry_filters.end(); ++i)
110  if ((*i)->match(e))
111  return true;
112  return false;
113  }
114 
115  virtual bool same_type_less(const text_delaf_entry_filter<Char, CaseNormalizer> &l) const
116  { return *this < dynamic_cast<const union_text_delaf_entry_filter<Char, CaseNormalizer> &>(l); }
117 
118  virtual std::ostream& serialize(std::ostream& out) const
119  {
120  if (delaf_entry_filters.empty())
121  return out;
122  typename ptr_list<text_delaf_entry_filter<Char, CaseNormalizer> >::const_iterator i(delaf_entry_filters.begin());
123  (*i)->serialize(out);
124  ++i;
125  for (; i != delaf_entry_filters.end(); ++i)
126  {
127  out << '+';
128  (*i)->serialize(out);
129  }
130  return out;
131  }
132 
133  virtual std::wostream& wserialize(std::wostream& out) const
134  {
135  if (delaf_entry_filters.empty())
136  return out;
137  typename ptr_list<text_delaf_entry_filter<Char, CaseNormalizer> >::const_iterator i(delaf_entry_filters.begin());
138  (*i)->wserialize(out);
139  ++i;
140  for (; i != delaf_entry_filters.end(); ++i)
141  {
142  out << L'+';
143  (*i)->wserialize(out);
144  }
145  return out;
146  }
147  };
